column5: I am very pleased to announce that Kyla Tooley from Espanola is the winner of our Extreme Angler - Muskie Print!!     Congrats again, and a very BIG thank you to Karl at Extreme Angler TV ( http://www.extremeanglertv.com ) for supplying such a generous prize!!
Congrats Kyla, that print will look great in the rec. room.   Mark
Congrats Kyla, that's a great looking print....,.if you don't have room for it I'm sure I could find a space on my wal  Maureen
Hey, congradulations Kyla. That's a great prize you won. If it doesn't fit in with your decor, I'd be happy to put it on my wall.
I wish that's on my outdoor card  Is that the similar style of painting with the current outdoor card? (Sm Bass)
